Package: networkanalytics
Repository: networkanalytics
Title: Network Analytics related functions 
Version: 1.0.0.0
Authors@R: person("Michael", "Mantfeld", email = "michael.mantfeld@ue.com.au", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: This package pulls data from the NAP API, draws graphs. To use the package a few environment variables need to be set up;
  nap_url - The url for the network analytics API that is to be used
  nap_phase_colours - Phase colour mapping to be used for graphing
  E.g
  Sys.setenv('nap_url'="http://rtssbx005.domain.dev.int:8889/")
  Sys.setenv('nap_phase_colours'="-=grey,1=red,2=blue,3=dark green")
Depends: R (>= 3.3.3)
